dmca.body:
Jonathan G. Fetterly (sbn 228612)
Holme Roberts & Oowen LLP 
777 S. Figueroa St. #2800
Los Angeles, Ca. 90017-5826

Attorney for plaintiffs- Sony BMG Music Entertainment; Arista Records LLC;& Interscope Records, Ca general partnership

United States District Court
 Central District of California 
    case no: CVO8-02794 AHM (JCx) 

Complaint for copyright infringement
 
vs

Lawrence D. Huey, D.D.S.,  Inc. ( Defendent)

  This internet provider address is my place of business, as i am the owner of a dental practice, which has 4 employees.  One of these employees downloaded the alleged copyright infringement w/o my permission or knowledge.  I have sent to the above attorney a declaration that i was not the involved party & would assist in identifying the alleged copyright infringement  user (responsible employee, since terminated).
The attorney responds only for $5,000.00 settlement. 
Any assistance would be appreciated...

Laurence D. Huey, DDS
